OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FCandidates standing in the Scottish
OL,8,FParliament election for this
OL,9,Fconstituency lay out their pledges to
OL,10,Fvoters.
OL,12,FMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,13,FLauderdale covers key Borders towns
OL,14,Fincluding Galashiels, Melrose, Lauder,
OL,15,FInnerleithen and Peebles.
OL,17,FThe seat has been held by the SNP for
OL,18,Fthe last 15 years.
OL,20,FITV Border has interviewed all the
OL,21,Fcandidates.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
