PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FThe Reform UK candidate for Midlothian
OL,8,FSouth, Tweeddale and Lauderdale has
OL,9,Ftold ITV Border that she doesn't
OL,10,F'necessarily believe in climate
OL,11,Fchange.'
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FPressed on the scientific consensus on
OL,8,Fthe impact of global warming, Carolyn
OL,9,FGrant, who is a wildlife photographer,
OL,10,Fsaid: "Maybe. The climate always
OL,11,Fchanges, the climate is better, the
OL,12,Fclimate's worse, it goes up by a few
OL,13,Fdegrees, it goes down by a few degrees
OL,14,Fby a period of a number of years, I
OL,15,Fstill don't believe necessarily
OL,16,Fspending money on it is always the
OL,17,Fanswer, nature will always have her
OL,18,Fway."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FReform UKs Holyrood manifesto includes
OL,8,Fa pledge to scrap all net zero targets
OL,9,Fand subsidies.
OL,11,FMs Grant also refused to fully condemn
OL,12,Ffar right activist Tommy Robinson,
OL,13,Fafter ITV Border reported that Senga
OL,14,FBeresford, another Reform UK
OL,15,Fcandidate, had backed him on social
OL,16,Fmedia.
OL,18,FMs Grant was asked about comments Mr
OL,19,FRobinson has made that have been
OL,20,Fdescribed as racist.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FShe said: "It's just a view, I don't
OL,8,Fthink anybody is truly racist but he
OL,9,Fjust has a view on certain matters."
OL,11,FTommy Robinson, whose real name is
OL,12,FStephen Yaxley-Lennon, has previously
OL,13,Fdenied being racist.
OL,15,FFormer Borders MP Calum Kerr is
OL,16,Fstanding to be the SNP candidate here.
OL,18,FHis predecessor Christine Grahame held
OL,19,Fthis seat from its creation in 2011.
OL,20,FShe retired at the end of last term.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FMr Kerr's shock win at the general
OL,8,Felection in 2015 was part of the SNP
OL,9,Flandslide. Two years later he lost the
OL,10,Fseat to Scottish Conservative John
OL,11,FLamont.
OL,13,FAsked about his party's stance that a
OL,14,Fmajority of SNP MSPs in the Scottish
OL,15,FParliament is a mandate for a second
OL,16,Findependence referendum, Mr Kerr said:
OL,17,F"I'm completely confident that there
OL,18,Fwill be a referendum if we win a
OL,19,Fmajority."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FThe UK Government's health secretary
OL,8,FWes Streeting reiterated their
OL,9,Fposition this week, that they will not
OL,10,Fgrant the powers to hold another poll
OL,11,Fon the issue.
OL,13,FIf the SNP falls short of a majority,
OL,14,FMr Kerr, who previously chaired Yes
OL,15,FScotland Borders, said he would
OL,16,Fcontinue to advocate for independence.
OL,18,FHe said: "I will still argue the case
OL,19,Fand we will have to see what happens.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FHe accepted that without a majority,
OL,8,Fthere would not be an "immediate
OL,9,Fopportunity" to hold another
OL,10,Freferendum.
OL,12,F"I think that then we haven't got the
OL,13,Fimmediate opportunity to do it, but it
OL,14,Fdoesn't mean that we won't have a
OL,15,Fstrong majority of independence
OL,16,Fsupport MSPs, I think that looks
OL,17,Fhighly likely."
OL,19,FScottish Conservatives
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
