FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FIn 2021, the Scottish Conservatives
OL,8,Fcame second here.
OL,10,FThe Midlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,11,FLauderdale constituency overlaps with
OL,12,FWestminster's Dumfriesshire,
OL,13,FClydesdale and Tweeddale. Scottish
OL,14,FConservative David Mundell has been
OL,15,Fthe MP there for two decades.
OL,17,FFormer Scottish Borders councillor
OL,18,FKeith Cockburn is standing on a
OL,19,Fpromise to cut taxes.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FHis party's manifesto promises to cut
OL,8,Fwelfare spending to pay for this. It
OL,9,Fincludes a pledge to introduce a two-
OL,10,Fchild limit on the Scottish Child
OL,11,FPayment. The weekly benefit is claimed
OL,12,Fby eligible families. The Scottish
OL,13,FGovernment estimates it keeps 40,000
OL,14,Fchildren out of poverty.
OL,16,FAsked about the policy, Mr Cockburn
OL,17,Fsaid: "I think it's all about making
OL,18,Fchoices and we're going to have to
OL,19,Fmake hard choices.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,F"When you look at the choice that
OL,8,Fworking people have to make as well,
OL,9,Fthey have to choose how many children
OL,10,Fthey can have, what they can afford.
OL,12,F"We're not saying that you can't have
OL,13,Fmore children and we are trying to
OL,14,Fhelp, and obviously the welfare state,
OL,15,FI think, is a good welfare state, but
OL,16,Fwhat we are saying is that we're going
OL,17,Fto have to make choices and we're
OL,18,Fgoing to have to try and help the
OL,19,Fpeople who are working too."
OL,21,FScottish Labour
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FThe Scottish Labour candidate Daniel
OL,8,FColeman has admitted "it's been
OL,9,Fdifficult" for his party since the UK
OL,10,FLabour government came to power.
OL,12,FMr Coleman stood in the 2024 general
OL,13,Felection in Dumfriesshire, Clydesdale
OL,14,Fand Tweeddale, where he came a close
OL,15,Fthird behind the Conservative and the
OL,16,FSNP.
OL,18,FSince then, Holyrood polling has
OL,19,Fsuggested Scottish Labour is lagging
OL,20,Fbehind the SNP.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FIn February, Scottish Labour leader
OL,8,FAnas Sarwar called on the prime
OL,9,Fminister to resign, saying the
OL,10,F"distraction needs to end."
OL,12,FMr Coleman backs Mr Sarwar's decision.
OL,13,FHe said: "It's been difficult, there's
OL,14,Fno doubt about that and mistakes have
OL,15,Fbeen made. Anas Sarwar has been very
OL,16,Fclear that mistakes have been made.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,F"I back Anas Sarwar. He made the call
OL,8,Fhe made, I understand why he made it.
OL,9,FBut we have to get back to the point
OL,10,Fthat this election is about Scotland,
OL,11,Fit's not about what's happening in
OL,12,FWestminster."
OL,14,FScottish Liberal Democrats
OL,16,FFormer charity boss Duncan Dunlop is
OL,17,Fstanding as the candidate for the
OL,18,FScottish Liberal Democrats.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FHe was chief executive of Who Cares?
OL,8,FScotland, which supports care
OL,9,Fexperienced people, and did
OL,10,Fpeacebuilding work in the Balkans
OL,11,Fbefore entering politics.
OL,13,FSpeaking at the Great Polish Map of
OL,14,FScotland in Eddleston, Mr Dunlop told
OL,15,FITV Border he wants the UK to rejoin
OL,16,Fthe EU.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FHe said: "We're here at the Great
OL,8,FPolish Map of Scotland and that for me
OL,9,Freally matters because one it's the
OL,10,Finternationalist perspective. And for
OL,11,Fme the EU and Europe and being bound
OL,12,Ftogether means it's far harder for us
OL,13,Fto hurt and go to conflict or war
OL,14,Fagainst each other."
OL,16,FThe Liberal Democrats came fourth in
OL,17,Fthis constituency in 2021, despite the
OL,18,FBorders once being a stronghold for
OL,19,Fthe party.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FMr Dunlop said: "We'll certainly do a
OL,8,Flot better than fourth and I think we
OL,9,Fcan win."
OL,11,FFull list of candidates standing in
OL,12,FMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,13,FLauderdale
OL,15,FKeith Cockburn, Scottish Conservative
OL,16,Fand Unionist Party
OL,18,FDaniel Coleman, Scottish Labour Party
OL,20,FDuncan Angus Melville Dunlop, Scottish
OL,21,FLiberal Democrats
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G17/24
