CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FCarolyn Grant, Reform UK
OL,9,FCalum Kerr, Scottish National Party
OL,10,F(SNP)
OL,12,FKey issues for voters in Midlothian
OL,13,FSouth, Tweeddale and Lauderdale
OL,15,FSupport for the arts is "vital" for
OL,16,Flocal health and wellbeing, according
OL,17,Fto the boss of the theatre in Peebles.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G18/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FFraser Morrison, executive and
OL,8,Fcreative director at the Eastgate
OL,9,FTheatre and Arts Centre, says they are
OL,10,Funder pressure from rising costs.
OL,12,F80,000 people a year visit the venue
OL,13,Fwhich offers a calendar of live music,
OL,14,Ftheatrical productions and arts events.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G19/24
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FMr Morrison said: "It is incredibly
OL,8,Fvital that arts centres like us at the
OL,9,Feastgate get that support from our
OL,10,Flocal government (and) national
OL,11,Fgovernment as well. Because without
OL,12,Fplaces like this our local people,
OL,13,Flocal economy, would not have the
OL,14,Faccess to that local arts and culture
OL,15,Fthat people we feel are vital for
OL,16,Fpeople's health and wellbeing."
OL,18,FThe constituency also attracts
OL,19,Fvisitors who come to mountain bike and
OL,20,Fcycle.
OL,26,@rD@RpmrD@Vpn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G20/24
