PN,35221
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776445554
OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FNext year, stage one of the Tour de
OL,8,FFrance will pass through the Borders
OL,9,Fon July 2.
OL,11,FThe world-famous race is expected to
OL,12,Fdraw a television audience of billions.
OL,14,FIn Galashiels, Angela Crow, who runs
OL,15,Fthe social enterprise Bike and Hike
OL,16,FHub, says the impact will be "huge."
OL,26,@xD@^OUxD@dO]
