OL,3,CThe battle for the Borders -
OL,4,CMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,5,CLauderdale
OL,7,FShe said: "At the moment, a lot of
OL,8,Fpeople see the Borders as a go through
OL,9,Frather than a go to and stay place and
OL,10,Fthere's a lot of organisations working
OL,11,Freally hard to change that perception.
OL,12,FWe'll be on the world stage and people
OL,13,Fwill want to come and find out a
OL,14,Flittle bit more about us because
OL,15,Fthere's a lot going on."
OL,17,F2021 results for Midlothian South,
OL,18,FTweeddale and Lauderdale
OL,20,FChristine Grahame - Scottish National
OL,21,FParty - 19,807 votes
